      <title>特朗普与主要贸易伙伴展开关税对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-barrels-toward-tariff-showdown-with-canada-mexico-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普准备于周六征收第一波关税，这将促使外国政府和企业纷纷避开潜在的关税并准备采取报复措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-barrels-toward-tariff-showdown-with-canada-mexico-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 00:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果战争增加数百万人感染疾病的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/war-in-congo-s-east-puts-millions-at-risk-of-infectious-disease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲首席卫生咨询机构表示，卢旺达支持的叛军与刚果军队之间的战斗已使数百万人面临因疾病蔓延而死亡的高风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/war-in-congo-s-east-puts-millions-at-risk-of-infectious-disease</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 16:42:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
